latestPosts.caption:
this girlies trip taught me so much. Just having a little peace of mind with all the girls who truly get me, who have been through similar things as me is so powerful. Being at the beach was incredibly therapeutic and it felt like the waves washed away all the clutter in my mind, leaving me clear and content. I felt a new version of myself rise up. i realize now that a girlies trip is a must, it’s not just about having fun, but about healing wounds I didn’t even know needed healing ❤️‍🩹 

.
.
